292
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:39,640
I've handled way more cases than you.

293
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:43,560
There's no end to cases.

294
00:13:44,280 --> 00:13:46,720
Handling fewer cases is a blessing.

295
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:47,600
So,

296
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:49,920
let me give you a piece of advice.

297
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:53,960
It's better to avoid trouble.

298
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:56,760
Let me tell you something too.

299
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:59,360
If one day we really don't have to handle cases,

300
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:01,770
that means there's peace on earth.

301
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:03,770
Don't you think?

302
00:14:07,280 --> 00:14:08,480
Here is the medicine.

303
00:14:08,680 --> 00:14:11,340
Make sure your father boils and takes it on time.

304
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:13,200
Don't let him stay cooped up at home.

305
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:14,530
He needs some fresh air.

306
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:16,660
It'll help his lungs recover faster.

307
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:19,440
But I don't have the money

308
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:20,560
to pay you for this.

309
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:21,760
No need to pay me back.

310
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:24,200
You deliver newspapers and messages for me,

311
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:25,730
and you bring me customers.

312
00:14:25,880 --> 00:14:27,340
Consider it your payment.

313
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:28,080
Really?

314
00:14:28,280 --> 00:14:29,480
Thank you, Master Wu.

315
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:32,280
I'm about the same age as your older sister.

316
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:33,610
Just call me Sister Yue.

317
00:14:33,680 --> 00:14:34,340
Sister Yue.

318
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:39,440
What are you doing here?

319
00:14:39,440 --> 00:14:40,320
I'm going home.

320
00:14:46,120 --> 00:14:47,440
Why are you following me?

321
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:48,480
Just keep walking.

322
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:49,810
Why do you care what I do?

323
00:14:50,280 --> 00:14:52,120
Having two police officers follow me

324
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:53,450
is really creepy, okay?

325
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:54,400
Fine.

326
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:58,160
We're going to Jiqing Lane on Fuyou Street.

327
00:14:58,600 --> 00:15:01,240
The kitchen at No. 7, Lane 18.

328
00:15:01,920 --> 00:15:03,000
What are you going there for?

329
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,660
That's none of your business.

330
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:07,200
I'm making it my business.

331
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:09,000
Fine. A prostitute reported it.

332
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:10,920
She said a customer beat her and didn't pay.

333
00:15:10,920 --> 00:15:11,840
She wants us to get justice.

334
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:12,920
It hurts!

335
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:14,800
Justice?

336
00:15:15,680 --> 00:15:17,540
Doesn't that happen all the time?

337
00:15:17,560 --> 00:15:18,960
For people at the bottom,

338
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:20,860
there is no such thing as justice.

339
00:15:32,120 --> 00:15:32,560
Chief,

340
00:15:33,040 --> 00:15:34,100
you asked to see me?

341
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:37,300
A charred body was found on Sanshui Road.

342
00:15:37,560 --> 00:15:40,280
That is Renjin Chamber of Commerce territory.

343
00:15:40,480 --> 00:15:42,720
Go check it out with Forensic Doctor Yang.

344
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:43,080
Okay.

345
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:45,440
I'll take Yao Zhidi with me right away.

346
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:45,880
Wait.

347
00:15:46,680 --> 00:15:47,560
Why bring her?

348
00:15:48,040 --> 00:15:49,480
In future homicide cases,

349
00:15:49,480 --> 00:15:51,040
don't let that woman get involved.
